1.1.0
  - Adjusted how the vault stats window is shown and hidden
  - Added a setting to auto show the vault stats window at the vault

1.0.2
  - Fixed a UI error that would occur when items were removed from the furnishing vault and then Vault Stats tried to update

1.0.1
  - Fixed a bug where the used vault amount would not show up when outside your houses

1.0.0
  - The Deposit Queue will save between UI reloads
  - Deposit same from house now waits for remove furniture request result before proceeding to the next item

0.3.0
  - Added a queue feature for adding items to the furniture vault
  - Added the vault stats module
  - Both the queue and vault stats modules can be completely unloaded in settings
  - Updated for 49

0.2.0
  - Made the retrieveto menu show up during more editor scenes
  - Added a function with keybind/slashcommand to store same items from house to furnishing vault
  - Added feature to be able to always send craftings stations to the furniture vault when retrieved
  - Added a settings menu
  - Added debugging information

0.0.2
  - Added function to store same items from inventory to the furnishing vault

0.0.1
